{"tid":1549643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[美領]入黎跟我讀一次 AUTONOMY，聽日要一路行一路講","createTime":"2019-09-07T11:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:53:41.000Z","uid":61101,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"79c3fcddb0bd8f36d1f0d209ac4bbb900554296b","tid":1549643,"uid":61101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:35:54.000Z","msg":"入黎跟我讀兩次<br />\n用US 口音讀一次<br />\n用UK口音讀一次<br />\n<a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/zht/詞典/英語-漢語-繁體/autonomy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdictionary.cambridge.org%2Fzht%2F%E8%A9%9E%E5%85%B8%2F%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E-%E6%BC%A2%E8%AA%9E-%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94%2Fautonomy&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=ce09e96a\" target=\"_blank\">https://dictionary.cambridge.org/zht/詞典/英語-漢語-繁體/autonomy</a><br />\n聽日要大大聲聲講俾國際聽香港人要求乜野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Demonstrators demanded immediate autonomy for their region.<br />\n遊行示威者要求立即實現該地區的自治。<br />\nThe universities want to preserve their autonomy from central government.<br />\n大學都希望維護其自主辦學權，不受中央政府的控制。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>寧化飛灰 不作浮塵<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5ecf98c34dbc938e661ebf6ece18f2417d321245","tid":1549643,"uid":61101,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"推一次讀一次<br />\nAUTONOMY"},{"pid":"ccd2a1b66d17049ec89b35bf60e35dd039fa016c","tid":1549643,"uid":194454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇下呢本外國文宣啊求下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n[重開] 美國就快復會！！快啲推比外國人睇！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90a7430f145a088c008dec05afdf6a7ca51eb9bb","tid":1549643,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:41:47.000Z","msg":"有D難讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9878b70ef970b8ff4897505ee09db133da3a6b08","tid":1549643,"uid":61101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a7430f145a088c008dec05afdf6a7ca51eb9bb","tid":1549643,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:41:47.000Z","msg":"有D難讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"一齊讀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7357e887b111b8033a6b085a29feed0546ab8de9","tid":1549643,"uid":61101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:52:07.000Z","msg":"推一次讀一次<br />\nAUTONOMY"},{"pid":"56fca0c7e916e1fee467a3312ed1217b6af8af8b","tid":1549643,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:54:02.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［拋磚］一人N個聽日用嘅英文口號<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549609</a>"},{"pid":"79ac7035b0c2bcf2d08e62f17033023e6d982df2","tid":1549643,"uid":60615,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"90a7430f145a088c008dec05afdf6a7ca51eb9bb","tid":1549643,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:41:47.000Z","msg":"有D難讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"顎湯奴咪"},{"pid":"bd5623900186ab9c57c4790de283e53590cecd6b","tid":1549643,"uid":61101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:00:39.000Z","msg":"推一次讀一次<br />\nAUTONOMY"},{"pid":"656811bf403d65f23b93ff0788385d1c38c676dd","tid":1549643,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"借之前一個巴打寫嘅文一用<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大搖大擺行出警察宿舍，<br />\n每一個警察行過，都陰陰嘴笑鳩你班香港人：<br />\n「光復香港喎，時代革命喎。」<br />\n「曱甴。」<br />\n<br />\n每一個圍過警署嘅街坊，<br />\n都要接受依一班警察，<br />\n仲有佢哋家屬嘅冷眼。<br />\n「嗰隻甴曱啊，」佢指住你，<br />\n「嗰日佢咪圍鳩咗喺到囉，<br />\n依家咪死狗咁。」<br />\n<br />\n你忍唔住，你屌鳩佢老母。<br />\n不過佢一啲都無怕過你，<br />\n「甴曱！收皮啦！你打鳩我啊？！」<br />\n佢行埋嚟，再摸下你個頭，<br />\n「戇鳩仔。」<br />\n你忍住，你知道你唔可能打返佢。<br />\n佢拍拍你塊臉，<br />\n「點啊？你唔打鳩我喇？」<br />\n佢一啲收手嘅意欲都無，<br />\n因為警察已經為所欲為：<br />\n「又話黑警死全家？我全家仲喺到喎。」<br />\n<br />\n宿舍隔離就係警署，<br />\n警察一嚟到就會將你搭入去。<br />\n無人知道裏面會發生咩事。<br />\n你可能會畀人打一身、<br />\n畀人彈春袋、玩屎忽。<br />\n你女朋友喺你隔離，<br />\n你唔知道佢畀人拉埋入去之後會發生咩事，<br />\n你保護唔到你女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n「我要你同我道歉。」<br />\n警察一家望實你，同你講。<br />\n你唔敢再生事端。<br />\n「對唔住，好對唔住。」<br />\n最後你向警察道歉。<br />\n佢一邊拍你塊臉，一邊同你講，<br />\n「下次唔好喇。」<br />\n你覺得好興幸，<br />\n警察肯原諒你。<br />\n<br />\n依一個就係香港人放棄嘅結局，<br />\n你班「曱甴」依家想放棄未？"},{"pid":"2cb74dcc7be5fae47ceb24a44c4cd6ddc63eb907","tid":1549643,"uid":49575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYFsNtt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYFsNtt.gif&h=9c453921&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef31e06dc7e8fc745722e5a269ea7fbc24698453","tid":1549643,"uid":61101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"推一次讀一次<br />\nAUTONOMY"},{"pid":"c8768e80afa71d4fd049feef19104e5f192be350","tid":1549643,"uid":222036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:08:04.000Z","msg":"屌 口號簡單啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>WE WANT AUTONOMY</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"